{"tid":2202924,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚耀宗稱被扣港人家屬如希望國際插手未必有好處","createTime":"2020-09-15T03:37:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T04:41:15.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9be79ae64ba25d80d31a93a39ed79c66921e647d","tid":2202924,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:37:46.000Z","msg":"12名涉嫌偷越國(邊)境犯罪的港人，被刑事拘留在深圳鹽田公安分局已20多天。<br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委譚耀宗在本台節目《千禧年代》說，家屬關心案件及希望特區政府協助，是很合理的事，但如果希望國際插手，未必對事情有好處。<br />\n<br />\n對於家屬委託的律師一直未能會見當事人，譚耀宗說，從公開資料得知，被拘留人士已經有官方委派的律師，因此不需要其他律師。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，偷越國(邊)境罪並非嚴重罪行，最多判囚一年，但未知調查期間會否發現相關人士有沒有牽涉其他罪行，至於其中一名涉嫌觸犯港區安全法的港人，會否由內地處理，則有待執法部門研究。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549670-20200915.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549670-20200915.htm&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacc3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=a7f23048\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549670-20200915.htm&h=29f47f64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549670-20200915.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7f68bbc8ef28b028d3875ab02bde8ff31692aa8b","tid":2202924,"uid":322732,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:42:41.000Z","msg":"咁香港又唔幫 支那更唔駛講<br />\n係咪要搵閰羅王幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461e90b652743530f444aa5f82b2889e7404442c","tid":2202924,"uid":310817,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:55:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0871ef474f813bd9dfa772d634fccf684451fa","tid":2202924,"uid":59461,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T03:57:44.000Z","msg":"好似電視劇d綁架劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3dd0bbe47ffe0a9acdc0d11118cfd28fd100588","tid":2202924,"uid":310817,"like":1,"dis